data.description: Country living at its finest and close to everything Chino Valley and the Tri cities have to offer. Gorgeous 3 bedroom 2 bath home on one acre with views for miles. If this is not enough, the home had a new roof in Aug 2023, solar was added in June 2022. Luxury vinyl wood floor throughout the home and new paint and A 1020sqft Detached Garage/shop for all your toys! The owner have paid attention to details that make a house a home. The home has an incredible energy and move in ready!
